Today we are releasing a Firefox Safe Search plugin[1]. The Safe Search plugin[2] allows you to easily search using safe search from the Firefox toolbar.

Installation:

1. Visit the firefox safe search plugin search results page[3] when using firefox
2. Click on Safe Search from Primary Technology
3. Click Add

